Blood Summoner									KEY:Summoner Archetype ~ Blood Summoner			CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.SummonerArchetype.SummonerShieldAlly.SummonerTransposition.SummonerGreaterShieldAlly.SummonerMergeForms																	PRECLASS:1,Summoner=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Summoner Archetype ~ Blood Summoner],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.SummonerShieldAlly,TYPE.SummonerTransposition,TYPE.SummonerGreaterShieldAlly,TYPE.SummonerMergeForms]								DESC:A blood summoner conjures an eidolon born from violence and blood.																																																																																																ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Blood Summoner ~ Blood Offering|PRECLASS:1,Summoner=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Blood Summoner ~ Blood Travel|PRECLASS:1,Summoner=8	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Blood Summoner ~ Fiendish Calling|PRECLASS:1,Summoner=10	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Blood Summoner ~ Blood Possession|PRECLASS:1,Summoner=16																																												CSKILL:Heal	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.24	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Summoner
Blood Offering									KEY:Blood Summoner ~ Blood Offering				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SummonerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.SummonerShieldAlly																																																																							DESC:The blood summoner can sacrifice a flask of fresh blood to aid and appease an evil outsider.																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.24
Blood Travel									KEY:Blood Summoner ~ Blood Travel				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SummonerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.SummonerTransposition																																																																						DESC:A blood summoner can use his maker's call ability to allow his eidolon to travel through the blood of other creatures instead of bringing it to his side. The eidolon can either emerge from the blood of a living creature within range that has fewer than its maximum hit points remaining, or burst from the corpse of a Small or larger creature within range that has been dead for no longer than 1 minute.																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.24
Fiendish Calling									KEY:Blood Summoner ~ Fiendish Calling			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SummonerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.SummonerGreaterShieldAlly																																																																						DESC:The blood summoner's summon monster ability can additionally be used as one of the planar binding spells, his level determining which version, but only to call evil outsiders.																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.24
Blood Possession									KEY:Blood Summoner ~ Blood Possession			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.SummonerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.SummonerMergeForms																																																																							DESC:as a full-round action, a blood summoner's eidolon can enter and control the body of any corporeal creature that has blood. This ability functions as marionette possession, except that the eidolon's body also enters the target and the target can be unwilling.																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.24

