Raging Cannibal									KEY:Barbarian Archetype ~ Raging Cannibal			CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.BarbarianArchetype.BarbarianUncannyDodge.BarbarianTrapSense.BarbarianImprovedUncannyDodge.BarbarianDamageReduction															PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Barbarian Archetype ~ Raging Cannibal],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.BarbarianUncannyDodge.BarbarianTrapSense.BarbarianImprovedUncannyDodge.BarbarianDamageReduction]								DESC:The raging cannibal is a barbarian who feasts upon her fallen opponents not out of hunger, or even a taste for flesh, but because she believes physically consuming her foes and defiling their lost lives demonstrates her strength.																																																																				ABILITY:Barbarian Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Raging Cannibal ~ Consume Vigor|PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=2	ABILITY:Barbarian Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Raging Cannibal ~ Intimidating Gouge|PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=3	ABILITY:Barbarian Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Raging Cannibal ~ Feed from Fury|PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=5	ABILITY:Barbarian Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Raging Cannibal ~ Razor-Toothed Fury|PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=6	ABILITY:Barbarian Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Raging Cannibal ~ Rage Powers|PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=1	ABILITY:Barbarian Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Rage Power ~ Animal Fury|PRECLASS:1,Barbarian=2	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Rage Power|-1			COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.27	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Barbarian
Consume Vigor									KEY:Raging Cannibal ~ Consume Vigor				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.ArchetypeAbility.BarbarianUncannyDodge																																																																			DESC:When a raging cannibal reduces a creature of the same creature type as herself to 0 or fewer hit points with her bite attack while raging, she can consume a chunk of its body to gain a portion of its power. When this occurs, the raging cannibal gains %1 additional rounds of rage, provided the creature's Hit Dice equal or exceed her barbarian level.|((BarbarianLVL)-1)/3																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.27
Intimidating Gouge								KEY:Raging Cannibal ~ Intimidating Gouge			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.ArchetypeAbility.BarbarianTrapSense																																																																				DESC:When a raging cannibal confirms a critical hit against a creature of the same creature type as herself with her bite attack while raging, she gains a +%1 bonus on Intimidate checks for the duration of the rage.|BarbarianLVL/2																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.27
Feed from Fury									KEY:Raging Cannibal ~ Feed from Fury			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.ArchetypeAbility.BarbarianImprovedUncannyDodge																																																																		DESC:When a raging cannibal confirms a critical hit against a creature of the same creature type as herself with her bite attack while raging, she gains %1 temporary hit points. These temporary hit points stack with other temporary hit points gained from this ability, but not with those from other sources. These temporary hit points fade after %2 minutes.|BarbarianLVL|BarbarianLVL*10																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.27
Razor-Toothed Fury								KEY:Raging Cannibal ~ Razor-Toothed Fury			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.ArchetypeAbility.BarbarianDamageReduction																																																																			DESC:When using her bite attack, the raging cannibal can take a -%1 penalty on her attack roll to add %2 points of bleed damage to the damage dealt.|((BarbarianLVL)-2)/4|(((BarbarianLVL)-2)/4)*2																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.27
Rage Powers										KEY:Raging Cannibal ~ Rage Powers				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:BarbarianClassFeatures.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality																																																																												DESC:The following rage powers complement the raging cannibal archetype: animal fury, internal fortitude, intimidating glare, primal scent, scent, and terrifying howl.																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.27

