Consume the Enemy									KEY:Domain Power ~ Consume the Enemy			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:As a full-round action that is considered an evil act and provokes attacks of opportunity, you can bite a helpless living or freshly killed creature, dealing 1d3 points of damage. By consuming the creature's flesh, you gain a +%1 profane bonus on saving throw DCs for all spells, spell-like abilities, and supernatural abilities you use against creatures of the same type (and subtype, if humanoid or outsider) as the cannibalized creature. This effect lasts for %2 minutes or until you use this ability against a different creature. You can use this ability %3 times per day.|((DomainEvilLVL/4)+1,5)|DomainEvilLVL/2|DomainEvilTimes																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.18	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DomainEvilTimes	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
Faith-Stealing Strike								KEY:Domain Power ~ Faith-Stealing Strike (Chaos)	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:You can make a single melee attack using your highest base attack bonus against a creature capable of casting divine spells. If you damage the creature, it must succeed at a Will save (DC %1) or be unable to cast any divine spells for 1 round. If you do not damage your target with the attack, this ability is expended with no effect. You can use this ability %2 times per day.|DomainChaosDC|DomainChaosTimes																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.19	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DomainChaosTimes	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
Faith-Stealing Strike								KEY:Domain Power ~ Faith-Stealing Strike (Evil)		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:You can make a single melee attack using your highest base attack bonus against a creature capable of casting divine spells. If you damage the creature, it must succeed at a Will save (DC %1) or be unable to cast any divine spells for 1 round. If you do not damage your target with the attack, this ability is expended with no effect. You can use this ability %2 times per day.|DomainEvilDC|DomainEvilTimes																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.19	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DomainEvilTimes	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
Hateful Aura									KEY:Domain Power ~ Hateful Aura				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:You can emit a 30-foot aura of hatred %1 rounds per day. These rounds need not be consecutive. Enemies within this aura must attempt a Will save (DC %2). Characters who fail their save are filled with hatred, and cannot consider other characters allies for the purpose of any actions or use any teamwork feats. The effect ends immediately if the creature leaves the aura, you end the aura as a free action, or you expend all rounds of this ability.|DomainDestructionLVL|DomainDestructionDC																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.19	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DomainDestructionLVL	ASPECT:CheckType|Rounds per Day
More for Me										KEY:Domain Power ~ More for Me				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:When another character within 30 feet casts a spell with a range greater than touch, you can attempt a caster level check as an immediate action (DC = 15 + the spell's level). If you succeed at the check, you receive the spell's benefit instead of one of the spell's intended targets (chosen by you). If you are already a target of the spell, you are affected as though you were targeted by the same spell twice. This ability does not grant you knowledge of the spell being cast. You can use this ability %1 times per day.|DomainTrickeryTimes																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.19	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DomainTrickeryTimes	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
Pain Is Power									KEY:Domain Power ~ Pain Is Power (Evil)			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:After taking damage from any source, you may attempt a DC 25 concentration check as an immediate action. If you succeed, you gain the benefits of a blessing of fervor spell for %1 rounds. If you fail, this ability is expended with no effect. You can use this ability %2 times per day.|DomainEvilLVL/2|(DomainEvilLVL-4)/4																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.19	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|(DomainEvilLVL-4)/4	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
Pain Is Power									KEY:Domain Power ~ Pain Is Power (Law)			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:After taking damage from any source, you may attempt a DC 25 concentration check as an immediate action. If you succeed, you gain the benefits of a blessing of fervor spell for %1 rounds. If you fail, this ability is expended with no effect. You can use this ability %2 times per day.|DomainLawLVL/2|(DomainLawLVL-4)/4																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.19	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|(DomainLawLVL-4)/4	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
Spark Malfeasance									KEY:Domain Power ~ Spark Malfeasance			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower																																																																														DESC:You can awaken the sinful desires of a target within 30 feet with a ranged touch attack. The target suffers extreme guilt and is sickened for %1 rounds. To end the effect earlier, the target can willingly commit an evil act (if it is of good alignment) or attempt a Will save (DC %2) at the beginning of its turn each round. Creatures that succeed at their saving throws are immune to this ability for 24 hours. You can use this ability %3 times per day.|CASTERLEVEL/2|(10+(CASTERLEVEL/2)+WIS)|(CASTERLEVEL-4)/4																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.18	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|(CASTERLEVEL-4)/4	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day

