Animal Fury, Greater								KEY:Rage Power ~ Animal Fury (Greater)			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.RagePower.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary									PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Rage Power ~ Animal Fury																																																					DESC:This power works as animal fury, but the barbarian's bite attack deals damage as if she were one size larger.																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.27	ASPECT:ChildAbility|Rage
Penetrating Bite									KEY:Rage Power ~ Penetrating Bite				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.RagePower.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary									PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Rage Power ~ Animal Fury																																														PREVARGTEQ:RagePowersLVL,4			DESC:When using the animal fury rage power while raging, the barbarian's bite is able to overcoming damage reduction. At 4th level, her bite is treated as a magic weapon. At 7th level, it is treated as cold iron and silver, and at 10th level, as a chaotic weapon. At 16th level, her bite is treated as an adamantine weapon for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction and bypassing hardness.																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.27	ASPECT:ChildAbility|Rage
Savage Jaw										KEY:Rage Power ~ Savage Jaw					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.RagePower.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary									PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Rage Power ~ Animal Fury																																																					DESC:While raging, the barbarian can open her jaw wide and latch her teeth firmly onto her opponent. While using the animal fury power, the barbarian can activate this power as a free action and gain the grab ability with her bite attack until the start of her next turn. This power can be used only once per rage.																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.27	ASPECT:ChildAbility|Rage
